title: Emma Stone makes her music video debut
text:
Emma Stone made her music video debut in Canadian rock group Arcade Fire's video for the song 'Anna.'
READ: Kate Winslet, Emma Stone in talks to star in ''The Favourite''
In the video, Emma can be seen walking in a cruise ship while shoving a fistful of notes in her mouth . The actress is currently working on the musical La La Land with her Crazy, Stupid, Love co-star Ryan Gosling.
